column2: select floor((p.petroMag_r - # - # * log1#(dbo.fCosmoDl(s.z)) - p.extinction_r)*#)/#, count(*) N from SpecObj s inner join PhotoObj p on s.bestObjID = p.ObjID where s.z > #  and s.z < # and p.petroMag_r - # - # * log1#(dbo.fCosmoDl(s.z)) - p.extinction_r > # group by floor((p.petroMag_r - # - # * log1#(dbo.fCosmoDl(s.z)) - p.extinction_r)*#) order by #
